Hello,
I am looking into ways to use JUNIT to test java projects developed using
rational rose real time.  Basically I want to be able to develop my Junit
tests as I develop my rational rose project.  Does anybody know of any of
useful documents that discuss this topic or have any useful ideas.

cheers

Nic
